name: Stranger Tings Oculus
description:
Stranger Tings Water Gate for Meta Quest 2.

Just a single level put together as sort off a 24hr Game Jam challenge. Also because me and my daughters just finished ST4 and they asked me to make a level, still thinking of going for a endless runner/beat saber level inspired by Max's run from vecna. but my main game is drawing me back.

90% of asset's from Sketchfab, credit given in game and also available on request on .txt form.

Loads of bugs and extras things I coulda/shoulda/woulda done if I gave this more time.

JKLe 'Vesconte

JKLabs 2022
